data.description: Picture this, you pull into your long driveway after a busy day of work. You park and walk through the gate and into your home through the backdoor. You look out your kitchen window and smile at your immaculate lawn. It's a beautiful fall evening, the kind you want to soak up before winter comes. It's just too beautiful outside not to enjoy! You last minute call your friends and invite them over to a bbq at your home. Before you know it, your backyard is filled with friends laughing on the covered patio. The smell of hotdogs and hamburgers on the grill fill the air and there is the sound of metal clanking in the background from your friends playing horseshoes. You look around and in this moment you are thankful you have this beautiful space to share with your friends. Life does't get any better than this. Now that's the picture you want to see isn't it?!
